365
00:23:25,980 --> 00:23:27,310
Cheng Xiao

366
00:23:28,020 --> 00:23:29,390
is a bit bad for you.

367
00:23:31,000 --> 00:23:32,860
Since you became her instructor,

368
00:23:32,880 --> 00:23:34,940
