369
00:23:35,030 --> 00:23:35,790
is coming.

370
00:23:40,510 --> 00:23:42,310
This is my duty as an instructor.

371
00:23:42,890 --> 00:23:45,010
The punishments you have received because of your students

372
00:23:45,010 --> 00:23:46,810
outnumber mine by a wide margin.

373
00:23:49,010 --> 00:23:50,810
You did a background check on me?

