my dream is about to shatter.

435
00:30:52,160 --> 00:30:54,080
I don't want to drag this out.

436
00:31:01,460 --> 00:31:02,990
I respect all your choices,

437
00:31:03,960 --> 00:31:05,740
but I hope you won't regret this

438
00:31:06,050 --> 00:31:07,450
when you think back on it.

439
00:31:26,310 --> 00:31:26,650
Okay.

440
00:31:27,490 --> 00:31:29,430
Then you can go be a pilot.

441
00:31:30,120 --> 00:31:31,780
Don't cry when the time comes.

442
00:31:40,270 --> 00:31:42,420
I won't give you another chance to get dirt on me.

443
00:31:42,420 --> 00:31:44,220
See you at the training grounds.

444
00:31:44,460 --> 00:31:45,790
You must keep every word

445
00:31:46,160 --> 00:31:46,870
you said.

446
00:31:47,040 --> 00:31:48,170
Not only will I do it,

447
00:31:48,540 --> 00:31:49,940
I will do better than you.

448
00:31:54,160 --> 00:31:54,690
Cai.

449
00:31:56,750 --> 00:31:57,130
What?

450
00:31:58,440 --> 00:31:59,340
I'll work hard

451
00:31:59,510 --> 00:32:00,910
when I get to the Passenger Flight Department.

452
00:32:00,910 --> 00:32:01,970
I will do you proud.

453
00:32:21,260 --> 00:32:21,860
Thank you.

454
00:32:23,140 --> 00:32:24,540
I've thought it through.

455
00:33:26,320 --> 00:33:27,580
I left something here.

456
00:33:28,790 --> 00:33:29,390
What is it?

457
00:33:31,180 --> 00:33:32,710
Can you open the door first?

458
00:33:53,040 --> 00:33:54,300
It's all Song's doing.

459
00:33:54,800 --> 00:33:55,610
It's a prank.

460
00:34:06,240 --> 00:34:06,900
Cheng Xiao,

461
00:34:09,550 --> 00:34:11,429
I’ve talked to Ground Handling.

462
00:34:12,250 --> 00:34:13,380
Report there first.

463
00:34:13,560 --> 00:34:14,400
Tomorrow,

464
00:34:14,440 --> 00:34:16,900
they will send someone to show you the ropes.

465
00:34:47,800 --> 00:34:48,449
Got it.

466
00:35:02,680 --> 00:35:04,180
[Cheng Xiao]

467
00:35:38,510 --> 00:35:39,770
What are you two doing?

468
00:35:39,870 --> 00:35:41,200
Are you watching me eat?

469
00:35:41,840 --> 00:35:42,490
Xiaoxiao,

470
00:35:43,320 --> 00:35:45,720
are you really going to do Ground Handling?

471
00:35:45,840 --> 00:35:47,160
It's only temporary.

472
00:35:47,840 --> 00:35:48,760
Xiao,

473
00:35:48,960 --> 00:35:49,960
Come on. Come on.

474
00:35:57,880 --> 00:35:58,610
Don't worry.

475
00:36:01,500 --> 00:36:03,230
I've been learning for so long,

476
00:36:03,920 --> 00:36:05,180
and flying for so long.

477
00:36:06,740 --> 00:36:08,140
I won't give up so easily.

478
00:36:12,720 --> 00:36:13,440
One day,

479
00:36:13,440 --> 00:36:15,220
I'll make Gu Nanting admit that

480
00:36:16,170 --> 00:36:17,210
I, Cheng Xiao,

481
00:36:19,160 --> 00:36:20,790
am qualified to be a pilot,

482
00:36:22,680 --> 00:36:23,480
and a captain.

483
00:36:47,560 --> 00:36:48,880
When I was playing with Wang Fan,

484
00:36:48,880 --> 00:36:50,480
I scored more than ten goals.

485
00:36:50,570 --> 00:36:51,440
Now that you've come,

486
00:36:51,440 --> 00:36:52,640
I've only gotten two.

487
00:36:53,960 --> 00:36:55,620
Defense is similar to flying.

488
00:36:56,050 --> 00:36:57,580
It depends on calm judgment

489
00:36:57,680 --> 00:36:59,140
to secure the bottom line.

490
00:37:00,800 --> 00:37:02,530
I remember when I first met you,

491
00:37:02,640 --> 00:37:04,830
you had just joined the school team in your freshman year.

492
00:37:04,830 --> 00:37:06,230
You loved attacking.

493
00:37:06,740 --> 00:37:09,270
You didn't respect the upperclassmen at all.

494
00:37:10,060 --> 00:37:11,360
I think that kind of brash attitude

495
00:37:11,360 --> 00:37:12,760
doesn't suit me anymore.

496
00:37:13,280 --> 00:37:13,840
Enough.

497
00:37:13,840 --> 00:37:15,190
Don't act innocent.

498
00:37:16,320 --> 00:37:20,010
You became the star player three months after joining the school team.

499
00:37:20,010 --> 00:37:22,230
I could only be a substitute.

500
00:37:25,860 --> 00:37:26,750
Do you know why?

501
00:37:30,260 --> 00:37:31,720
For four years in college,

502
00:37:31,860 --> 00:37:34,120
I only had one pair of knockoff sneakers.

503
00:37:35,910 --> 00:37:37,510
My family was poor back then.

504
00:37:37,840 --> 00:37:38,920
I didn't want to run too much

505
00:37:38,920 --> 00:37:40,410
in those pair of shoes.

506
00:37:40,870 --> 00:37:42,700
The coach could only bench me.

507
00:37:46,950 --> 00:37:49,680
People thought it was because you had no stamina.

508
00:37:52,480 --> 00:37:53,280
I was young

509
00:37:53,890 --> 00:37:55,290
and easily embarrassed.

510
00:37:57,590 --> 00:37:58,390
You know what?

511
00:37:59,200 --> 00:38:00,760
My first pair of authentic sneakers

512
00:38:00,760 --> 00:38:02,620
was the birthday gift you gave me.

513
00:38:04,380 --> 00:38:05,580
That pair of shoes...

514
00:38:05,720 --> 00:38:06,840
Every time I finished playing,

515
00:38:06,840 --> 00:38:08,440
I would wipe them clean

516
00:38:09,230 --> 00:38:10,520
before ever so carefully

517
00:38:10,520 --> 00:38:12,520
putting them back into the shoe box.

518
00:38:13,180 --> 00:38:15,040
At that time, I thought to myself,

519
00:38:15,230 --> 00:38:16,030
one day,

520
00:38:16,320 --> 00:38:19,320
I will achieve the financial freedom to buy sneakers.

521
00:38:19,850 --> 00:38:21,880
Now, the sneakers freedom of the entire Maintenance Department

522
00:38:21,880 --> 00:38:23,050
is yours.

523
00:38:26,010 --> 00:38:28,160
Let's go. I'll buy you a meal to celebrate.

524
00:38:28,160 --> 00:38:29,090
Celebrate what?

525
00:38:30,120 --> 00:38:31,560
Didn't your Maintenance Department just receive

526
00:38:31,560 --> 00:38:33,690
the outstanding contribution award?

527
00:38:34,030 --> 00:38:36,080
You really care about me, young man.

528
00:38:56,830 --> 00:38:57,690
I'm exhausted.

529
00:38:58,150 --> 00:38:59,570
The last two boxes.

530
00:39:09,420 --> 00:39:10,150
I'm new here.

531
00:39:10,400 --> 00:39:11,330
Nice to meet you.

532
00:39:12,200 --> 00:39:13,600
Stop it.

533
00:39:13,840 --> 00:39:14,750
I just want

534
00:39:14,830 --> 00:39:17,690
to learn more from you.

535
00:39:18,120 --> 00:39:18,960
Don't stand on ceremony.

536
00:39:18,960 --> 00:39:20,560
Let's learn from each other.

537
00:39:21,950 --> 00:39:23,010
By the way, Xiazhi,

538
00:39:23,320 --> 00:39:25,380
I want to discuss something with you.

539
00:39:25,550 --> 00:39:26,350
It's just...

540
00:39:27,280 --> 00:39:29,110
can we sleep in the same room?

541
00:39:33,760 --> 00:39:34,740
What do you mean?

542
00:39:35,030 --> 00:39:36,500
I have my own room...

543
00:39:38,680 --> 00:39:39,510
I just...

544
00:39:39,790 --> 00:39:41,850
I often have nightmares when I sleep.

545
00:39:42,350 --> 00:39:43,110
I'm scared.

546
00:39:45,810 --> 00:39:48,810
So you're a scaredy-cat...

547
00:39:51,000 --> 00:39:51,930
It's no big deal.

548
00:39:52,630 --> 00:39:53,400
I'll protect you.

549
00:39:53,400 --> 00:39:55,110
I was born to ward off evil.

550
00:39:55,500 --> 00:39:57,760
Ghosts and spirits dare not come near me.

551
00:39:58,750 --> 00:39:59,850
Thank you.

552
00:40:00,720 --> 00:40:01,600
I've cleaned the room.

553
00:40:01,600 --> 00:40:02,720
Do you want to go take a look?

554
00:40:02,720 --> 00:40:03,790
Lead the way!

555
00:40:09,480 --> 00:40:11,880
This is the bathroom in the master bedroom.

556
00:40:15,530 --> 00:40:17,400
There's even room service?

557
00:40:20,960 --> 00:40:23,030
Your bed is so clean.

558
00:40:23,320 --> 00:40:25,590
My mom always says my bed is like a pigsty.

559
00:40:26,700 --> 00:40:28,800
It's okay. I'll teach you how to make your bed.

560
00:40:28,800 --> 00:40:30,800
When we upgrade to the first class

561
00:40:30,800 --> 00:40:32,330
and go on long haul flights,

562
00:40:32,750 --> 00:40:35,170
we'll need to learn how to fold blankets anyway.

563
00:40:35,170 --> 00:40:37,200
Yuheng, you're too sweet.

564
00:40:37,780 --> 00:40:39,660
Your boyfriend is so lucky.

565
00:40:40,630 --> 00:40:42,230
I don't have a boyfriend yet.

566
00:40:43,590 --> 00:40:45,790
Stop acting.

567
00:40:46,300 --> 00:40:47,600
Everyone knows your boyfriend.

568
00:40:47,600 --> 00:40:49,450
is Captain Gu.

569
00:40:49,480 --> 00:40:50,730
He's not.

570
00:40:51,540 --> 00:40:53,370
No, you misunderstood.

571
00:40:53,880 --> 00:40:55,920
We were close when we were kids.

572
00:40:55,920 --> 00:40:57,920
We haven't seen each other in years.

573
00:40:58,440 --> 00:40:59,720
That's why we reconnected

574
00:40:59,720 --> 00:41:01,650
